                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新茶饮内卷，“国风茶饮黑马”霸王茶姬凭何突围？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">New&#160;tea&#160;drink&#160;inside&#160;the&#160;roll,&#160;&quot;national&#160;wind&#160;tea&#160;drink&#160;dark&#160;horse&quot;&#160;CHAGEE&#160;with&#160;how&#160;to&#160;break&#160;through?</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">于剑乔，刘嘉慧</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">天津大学</td>
                            </tr>
