                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京茶姬餐饮管理有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">霸王茶姬；STP战略；营销策略；新媒体；情感营销理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CHAGEE;&#160;STP&#160;strategy;&#160;Marketing&#160;strategy;&#160;New&#160;media;&#160;Emotional&#160; marketing&#160;theory</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">近年来，新茶饮市场增长迅速，已经达到千亿市场规模。但茶饮行业由于入局门槛较低、同质化程度高而被认为竞争最为激烈。从2020年开始，火爆数年的新茶饮赛道受到严重冲击，众多连锁茶饮品牌出现市值缩水乃至闭店等危机。不过2017年才成立的霸王茶姬在此期间却逆势增长令人刮目相看。短短6年间，“出海”成功，全球门店超过3000家。本案例以“奶茶新贵”霸王茶姬为研究对象，描述了霸王茶姬的成长发展史，详细介绍了其在发展过程中的STP战略和营销策略，探讨霸王茶姬成功背后的商业逻辑，旨在引导学生学习和掌握在新媒体时代有关产品定位和营销推广策略的理论知识以及在实践中的应用。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In&#160;recent&#160;years,&#160;the&#160;new&#160;tea&#160;market&#160;has&#160;grown&#160;rapidly,&#160;and&#160;has&#160;reached&#160;100&#160;billion&#160;market&#160;scale.&#160;However,&#160;the&#160;tea&#160;industry&#160;is&#160;considered&#160;to&#160;be&#160;the&#160;most&#160;competitive&#160;because&#160;of&#160;its&#160;low&#160;entry&#160;threshold&#160;and&#160;high&#160;degree&#160;of&#160;homogenization.&#160;Starting&#160;from&#160;2020,&#160;the&#160;new&#160;tea&#160;track&#160;that&#160;has&#160;been&#160;hot&#160;for&#160;several&#160;years&#160;has&#160;been&#160;seriously&#160;impacted,&#160;and&#160;many&#160;chain&#160;tea&#160;brands&#160;have&#160;suffered&#160;crises&#160;such&#160;as&#160;shrinking&#160;market&#160;value&#160;and&#160;even&#160;closing&#160;stores.&#160;However,&#160;CHAGEE,&#160;which&#160;was&#160;only&#160;established&#160;in&#160;2017,&#160;has&#160;bucked&#160;the&#160;trend&#160;of&#160;growth&#160;during&#160;this&#160;period.&#160;In&#160;just&#160;6&#160;years,&#160;&quot;going&#160;to&#160;sea&quot;&#160;has&#160;been&#160;successful,&#160;with&#160;more&#160;than&#160;3,000&#160;stores&#160;worldwide.&#160;This&#160;case&#160;takes&#160;&quot;milk&#160;tea&#160;upstart&quot;&#160;CHAGEE&#160;as&#160;the&#160;research&#160;object,&#160;describes&#160;the&#160;development&#160;history&#160;of&#160;CHAGEE,&#160;introduces&#160;in&#160;detail&#160;its&#160;STP&#160;strategy&#160;and&#160;marketing&#160;strategy&#160;in&#160;the&#160;development&#160;process,&#160;discusses&#160;the&#160;business&#160;logic&#160;behind&#160;CHAGEE&#39;s&#160;success,&#160;and&#160;aims&#160;to&#160;guide&#160;students&#160;to&#160;learn&#160;and&#160;master&#160;the&#160;theoretical&#160;knowledge&#160;of&#160;product&#160;positioning&#160;and&#160;marketing&#160;promotion&#160;strategy&#160;in&#160;the&#160;new&#160;media&#160;era&#160;and&#160;its&#160;application&#160;in&#160;practice.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《市场营销》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STP理论；4P理论；社会化媒体营销理论；情感营销理论；SWOT分析法</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
